      <title>欧盟谈判暂停后，格鲁吉亚爆发抗议冲突，40 多人住院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-01/over-40-people-hospitalized-in-georgia-during-protests-over-suspension-of-eu-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚第比利斯（美联社）——官员周日称，格鲁吉亚首都爆发抗议活动已连续第三晚，抗议政府中止加入欧盟谈判的决定，导致 44 人住院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-01/over-40-people-hospitalized-in-georgia-during-protests-over-suspension-of-eu-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 12:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚发动反击，试图制止叛乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-01/syria-sends-in-reinforcements-to-halt-insurgents-from-advancing-after-seizing-aleppo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝鲁特（美联社）——叙利亚军队周日向西北部增派部队并发动空袭，试图击退占领该国最大城市阿勒颇的叛乱分子，而伊朗承诺协助政府抵御这次突然进攻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-01/syria-sends-in-reinforcements-to-halt-insurgents-from-advancing-after-seizing-aleppo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 10:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
